HEADWORD: Ultimately
<hw>Ul"ti*mate*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>As a final
consequence; at last; in the end; <as>as, afflictions often tend to
correct immoral habits, and <ex>ultimately</ex> prove
blessings</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

